        public final ManagementEntityType getColumnType(java.lang.String columnName)
        Returns the type of the column.

        There is only two available column names:

        • INDEX_COLUMN_NAME that represents column containing array index.
        • VALUE_COLUMN_NAME that represents column containing array element.
